recode - gist clone

* ABOUT

Recode is gist clone. You can paste your code and share it with your friends.

* REQUIREMENT

- git

- CPAN modules

  Cwd
  Digest::SHA1
  Encode
  HTML::Entities
  Mojolicious::Lite
  Path::Class
  URI::Escape

* USAGE

- Run recode.pl as a daemon.

  % ./recode.pl daemon

- Run git-daemon. YOUR_REPOS_PATH is 'bare' in default.
  'bare' directory was created when recode.pl runs.

  % git daemon --export-all --enable=receive-pack --base-path=YOUR_REPOS_PATH
